en_189779_0	Lakshman Seneviratne's Ministerial position has been amended.
en_189779_1	He was first sworn in as State Minister of Public Administration and Management, and Law and Oder.
en_189779_2	However, later the President's Media Division announced that Seneviratne's position was amended.
en_189779_3	His new posting is State Minister of Science, Technology and Research, Skills Development and Vocational Training, and Hill Country Heritage.
